Support

I support a handful of ways you can get support across my network of APIs, and research projects. I prefer to keep all information associated with each projects Github repository, but also try and make myself as available as possible via other channels.

via Github via Twitter via Email

Please remember I am a one person show, and while I work to achieve the highest levels of available, there are times I go heads down on work, and tune out general email & social chatter. Usually if you submit via Github, with the right title, it will grab my attention, if its critical.
